.vscode/**
.gitignore
**/*.map
**/.DS_Store
.git/**
# NOTE: do NOT ignore bin/ — the fork's bundle-forge.sh stages the forge engine
# into bin/ and it MUST ship with the built-in extension (the bootstrap also does
# a post-gulp copy as a belt-and-suspenders guarantee). The repo has no bin/, so
# this doesn't bloat a from-source .vsix.
